The dynamic misalignment forces and moments are treated as excitations on the rotor and only the 1X, 2X, 3X, and 4X harmonic components are considered, as given below
(10){Qc 1}={Fx1(sin(ωt)+sin(2ωt)+sin(3ωt)+sin(4ωt))Fy1(cos(ωt)+cos(2ωt)+cos(3ωt)+cos(4ωt))My1(sin(ωt)+sin(2ωt)+sin(3ωt)+sin(4ωt))Mx1(cos(ωt)+cos(2ωt)+cos(3ωt)+cos(4ωt))}

(11){Qc 2}={Fx2(sin(ωt)+sin(2ωt)+sin(3ωt)+sin(4ωt))Fy2(cos(ωt)+cos(2ωt)+cos(3ωt)+cos(4ωt))My2(sin(ωt)+sin(2ωt)+sin(3ωt)+sin(4ωt))Mx2(cos(ωt)+cos(2ωt)+cos(3ωt)+cos(4ωt))}
